{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "title",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# Deep Silicon Architecture — Omni-Operator on Apple Silicon\n\nMaster map of the Mavis-Apex-Architecture ported to Apple Silicon native.\nGenerated 2026-06-02 from Operation Deep Silicon.\n\n**The thesis:** The Omni-Operator is a Mac. Zero latency = UMA. Infinite context = PagedEviction + Anchor-Ends + Ring Attention. Safety = microVM per task + Reflection layer. The model is the engine; the hardware is the thin deterministic I/O layer.",
      "x": -2000,
      "y": -2200,
      "width": 4000,
      "height": 200,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "group-hardware",
      "type": "group",
      "label": "Hardware Layer (Apple Silicon)",
      "x": -2000,
      "y": -1900,
      "width": 4000,
      "height": 700,
      "color": "1",
      "background": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "group-sandbox",
